text = "Red Shadow — Vertical Loop Prototype
[Wall Climb] In a narrow shaft, hold Left/Right into the wall and tap Space to kick off both walls and climb!
Up the left shaft -> top bridge -> down the right platforms -> loop the floor
A/D : Move    Space : Jump (double)    Shift : Dash
S : Flip    L : Blink    C : Stealth    J/LMB : Sword"
